@1091 = ~I have mastered the power within me and held the evil in check, but I know as well... if not better... then most of my brethren the threat that it holds for all of Faerûn. I will not allow this. I have dedicated my life to preventing it.~
@1161 = ~I make no judgement upon you, <CHARNAME>. You are what you were born to be. I can only trust myself to hold to the path of good that will lead to the destruction of the true evil that threatens Faerûn. There is no other path for me.~
